name: lean concrete production, with cement CEM II/A | lean concrete | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/12524/documentation

This datasets contains the production of lean concrete with cement CEM II/A from primary aggregates (no input of recycled gravel or sand).;Density: 2250 kg/m3, content of cement: 150 kg/m3;Exposition class according to EN 206-1: no normative requirements;Examples fo this exposition class are blinding layers below foundations.

The activity starts with the ingredients for the concrete at the factory gate.

Includes the whole manufacturing processes to produce ready-mixed concrete, internal processes (transport, etc.) and infrastructure. No administration is included.
